The server use POE lib.
You should install the lib with command
 $sudo apt-get install -y libmoosex-poe-perl



Protocol

%s% - separator of protocol

    -a                                                  -get adress client and server
    -t                                                  -get time of server
    -f-g%_%<path>                                       -get file  by $path
    -f-s%_%<path>%_%<name>%_%<content>                  -save file to server by $path
    -c-s                                                -connected success
    -f-s-s                                              -file saved in server success
    -f-s-f                                              -file saved in server Failed
    -f-g-s%_%<name>%_%<content>                  -file from server
    -f-g-f%_%<error>                                    -get file from server finish with error



Example
 -f-s%_%/home/UserName/Uni/4_1/Perl/perl-labs/NetworkTechnology/ApplicationLayerProtocol/Client/Content/fileClient.txt%_%fileTest
    save file fileClient.txt and save as fileTest
 -f-g%_%Content/fileTest - get file fileTest from Server;
